      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, complete with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS. This specimen utilizes the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox paired with a factory limited-slip differential. To ensure structural and mechanical longevity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced and the rod bearings have been replaced. The suspension maintains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings for precise turn-in, while the Nappa leather interior shows only light patina consistent with careful use. This is a mechanically sorted example optimized for the purist who values chassis dynamics and atmospheric induction over showroom-floor aesthetics.",
